description: This Chainlink VRF common Parvati purrs with a rating of 21, and a multiplier of 3x. It has a total score of 63, and confers the same amount of votes in the EtherCats DAO. The card game properties are 8 for North, 2 for East, Stringalong for South, and Nine Lives for West. Parvati has the personality suit of punter. Each Founders Series cat is part of NFT history. These fine felines represent the first verifiably random packs minted with Chainlink VRF.
name: Parvati [63 Votes, Common]
